{"tid":2206241,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實香港有四百五十萬中立撚","createTime":"2020-09-17T11:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T14:47:55.000Z","uid":239942,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ac9e2ac9e5a6cda3abe33e220986be069bd921","tid":2206241,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"唔好成日FF二百萬黄可以推翻政府<br />\n香港主要三group人<br />\n泛黄: 200萬<br />\n紅加藍: 100萬<br />\n中立港豬 : 450萬<br />\n睇唔到贏嘅希望<br />\nUnless我地令果450萬都加入黄果邊<br />\n先有可能令政府跪<br />\n二百萬草根加中產對五百五十萬中立港豬加藍絲廢老加中共<br />\n冇得打"},{"pid":"64ce1002167ace5d8d9389452d4aae42fe1d62ec","tid":2206241,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"e92d43988035dfaa593e7eddb8d613c1eb5ae342","tid":2206241,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64ea4c0c218a4308af0235fda9301e5318781afe","tid":2206241,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e92d43988035dfaa593e7eddb8d613c1eb5ae342","tid":2206241,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"中立叫講黄，但默許不公義發生<br />\n係幫兇"},{"pid":"3038045900cd7e8ddfcf38af3a32eeef9d311e63","tid":2206241,"uid":282637,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"中咩立,只係一班不問世事,只識食玩痾訓嘅人形豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4802fa20ac94c54bc